    "summary": {
      "value": "Increase the potency of Drain spells."
    },
    "description": "<blockquote><p><strong>Requirements:</strong> you must have mastered one or more Classes among <strong>Entropist </strong>and <strong>Necromancer</strong>, and must have learned both the <strong>Drain Spirit</strong> and <strong>Drain Vigor</strong> spells.</p></blockquote><p>When you cast the @UUID[Compendium.projectfu.spells.Item.300SqWOqTrc7Qb3L]{Drain Spirit} or @UUID[Compendium.projectfu.spells.Item.HCknXFHu7q0bJ2Cg]{Drain Vigor} spells, the amount of Mind Points or Hit Points you recover is <strong>equal </strong>to the MP or HP loss suffered by the target, respectively (instead of being halved).</p><p>Additionally, your <strong>Drain Spirit</strong> causes the target to lose<strong>【HR + 20】</strong> Mind Points if you are <strong>level 20 or higher</strong>, or <strong>【HR + 25】</strong> Mind Points if you are <strong>level 40 or higher</strong>, instead of the normal<strong>【HR + 15】</strong>.</p>",
